<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <title><%= imgName %>  (<%= imgWidth %> x <%= imgHeight %>)</title>
</head>
<style>
    html {
        height: 100vh;
        width: 100vw
    }

    body {
        height: 100%;
        width: 100%;
        background-color: #212529;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
    }

    #done-info {
        display: inline-block;
        border-bottom: 3px solid rgb(14, 252, 240);
        font-weight: bold;
        font-size: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .img-name {
        color: rgb(14, 252, 240);
    }

    p {
        margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
</style>
<body>
    <div id="main" class="container text-light">
        <span id="done-info">Done!</span>
        <p><%= info %></p>
        <p>check your <b class="img-name"><%= imgName %></b> resized image within the <b>'images'</b> folder in the <b>'thumb'</b> folder  under the <b class="img-name">"<%= imgName %>-<%= imgWidth %>-<%= imgHeight %>-thumb.png"</b> name :)</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>